OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fdry in the evening with some
OL,7,Fbrightness at first. It will become
OL,8,Fincreasingly cloudy overnight with
OL,9,Fsome showery outbreaks of rain
OL,10,Fdeveloping.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FIt will be cloudy throughout
OL,13,Fthe day with showery outbreaks of
OL,14,Frain, these turning heavy in places.
OL,15,FFeeling much cooler than recent days.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
